2026-05-10T23:36:08.5431695Z 13    <!--
2026-05-10T23:36:08.5432283Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-10T23:36:08.5433147Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
